<P><H1 align=center>ADDRESS SUMMARY – DC060</H1>
<P></P>
<P><FONT color=red><STRONG>NOTE: </STRONG>areas shown in red are mandatory and must be completed to 
proceed</FONT>           </P>
<P>This screen shows a summary of the applicant’s address details - customer 
name, address type, address and dates resident in the property. The address 
already entered will already show in the main box</P>
<P><H3>Add: </H3>depending on the <A HREF="HELP_MortgageTerms.asp#LendingCriteria">lending criteria</A>, the 
applicant’s previous address details may need to be taken if the time at the 
current residence has been less than, for example, 3 years. To add a previous 
address, click on ‘Add’. This leads to <A HREF="HELP_DC065.asp">‘Address Details’ (DC065)</A>.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Edit: </H3>click on ‘Edit’ to access the details 
already entered for the current address. This will lead to <A HREF="HELP_DC065.asp">‘Address Details’ 
(DC065)</A>, where the missing information required on this screen can be completed
<P></P>
<P><H3>Delete: </H3>to delete a record entered, highlight it 
and click on ‘Delete’ 
<P></P>
<P>Applicant Correspondence Salutation: this field is populated with the details 
from ‘title’ and ‘surname’. It can be edited if required</P>
<P><H3>OK: </H3>when details of all relevant addresses have 
been completed, click on ‘OK’ to proceed to the next screen. – <A HREF="HELP_DC070.asp">Existing / 
Previous Mortgages (DC070)</A>
<P></P>

